Time-efficient kitchen workflows
Ingredient overlap maximization across meals
Macro-aligned meal portioning

Methodologies & Frameworks
Prep Models: Full batch (Sunday prep), Component prep (proteins/grains/veggies separate), Hybrid prep
Budget Systems: Cost-per-meal tracking, Seasonal produce prioritization, Generic vs. brand analysis
Storage: Glass container systems, Freezer rotation (FIFO), Labeling protocols, Shelf-life guidelines
Planning: Template week approach, Rotating 4-week menu, Flexible component system
Grocery: Organized by store section, Online order optimization, Bulk buying ROI analysis
Time Management: Parallel cooking (oven + stovetop + passive), Shared base ingredients

